spanGrp.span: When it’s the Saint Maria’s day our people go to the church in the morning.
bizım halh mm me meriamana güni oki olir giderlär tezdän kisläya yahierlär mum
Then they get together and bring food.
aa soradan gälierlär toplanierlär barabar gätırierlär emahlari
They dance together and celebrate this day.
People were going to the church to light a candle.
mm halh girierdi kisläya yahierdılär mum
And they were cooking it next to the church.
